**UiTest.exe** — Standalone RmlUi integration test suite (`tests/UiContextTest.cpp`). 20 assertions across 5 test groups, all passing:

| Test | What it proves |
|------|---------------|
| Version and initialization | RmlUi 6.2 library loads and initializes with stub interfaces. |
| Create and destroy a context | `Rml::CreateContext` returns a valid context with correct name and dimensions. Clean destruction. |
| Load RML document from memory | Full document lifecycle: load HTML from string, query title, find element by ID, verify tag name and ID. Proves the CSS/HTML parser and DOM work. |
